"time writing this the latest image is v92."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../driver-api/mtd/spi-intel.rst:31
msgid ""
"Install mtd-utils package [2]. We need this in order to erase the SPI serial "
"flash. Distros like Debian and Fedora have this prepackaged with name \"mtd-"
"utils\"."
