#: ../../../driver-api/mtd/spi-intel.rst:35
msgid ""
"Add \"spi_intel.writeable=1\" to the kernel command line and reboot the "
"board (you can also reload the driver passing \"writeable=1\" as module "
"parameter to modprobe)."
msgstr ""

